OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780510265
OL,3,CCo-accused 'misplaced' trust in
OL,4,Cpartner accused of baby murder, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe co-accused partner of a man
OL,8,Falleged to have murdered their adopted
OL,9,Fbaby son has told a jury his trust in
OL,10,Fhim was "misplaced."
OL,12,FJohn McGowan-Fazakerley, 32, is said
OL,13,Fto have caused or allowed the death of
OL,14,F13-month-old Preston Davey, along with
OL,15,Fchild cruelty and a sexual assault.
OL,17,FHis partner, high school teacher Jamie
OL,18,FVarley, 37, is accused of the murder
OL,19,Fof the youngster and multiple offences
OL,20,Fof cruelty and child sexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
