OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780510265
OL,3,CCo-accused 'misplaced' trust in
OL,4,Cpartner accused of baby murder, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FBoth men deny a sexual interest in the
OL,8,Fbaby and have pleaded not guilty to
OL,9,Fall charges at Preston Crown Court.
OL,11,FThe couple adopted "sweet and bubbly"
OL,12,FPreston in April 2023.
OL,14,FIt is alleged Preston was routinely
OL,15,Fill-treated, had indecent images and
OL,16,Fvideos taken of him, and was sexually
OL,17,Fabused and physically assaulted during
OL,18,Fthe four months Preston was living at
OL,19,Ftheir Blackpool home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780510265
OL,3,CCo-accused 'misplaced' trust in
OL,4,Cpartner accused of baby murder, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FOn the second day of the trial, sales
OL,8,Fmanager McGowan-Fazakerley told the
OL,9,Fjury he had no reason to believe
OL,10,FVarley had harmed Preston and thought
OL,11,Fhe had drowned after Varley told him
OL,12,Fen route to hospital that he had left
OL,13,Fhim alone in the bath.
OL,15,FHe said he still believed his death
OL,16,Fwas accidental as the couple continued
OL,17,Fto live with each other up until they
OL,18,Fwere re-arrested in 2025 and then both
OL,19,Fcharged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780510265
OL,3,CCo-accused 'misplaced' trust in
OL,4,Cpartner accused of baby murder, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMcGowan-Fazakerley's barrister Anne
OL,8,FWhyte KC said: "Prior to standing
OL,9,Ftrial at this building last month, had
OL,10,Fyou reached a stage where you truly
OL,11,Ffelt you understood what happened to
OL,12,FPreston that day?"
OL,14,FHe said "No, no. I don't think I fully
OL,15,Funderstood why he is not here."
OL,17,FMs Whyte then asked: "At the point of
OL,18,Fbeing charged were you still depending
OL,19,Fon what Mr Varley told you about the
OL,20,Fday?"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780510265
OL,3,CCo-accused 'misplaced' trust in
OL,4,Cpartner accused of baby murder, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"Yes", he said.
OL,9,FMs Whyte asked: "While on remand were
OL,10,Fyou still depending on what Mr Varley
OL,11,Ftold you about the day?"
OL,13,F"Yes", he said.
OL,15,FMcGowan-Fazakerley said he thinks he
OL,16,Fis starting to understand more about
OL,17,Fwhat happened, and said "I feel like
OL,18,Fmy trust in Jamie has been misplaced."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780510265
OL,3,CCo-accused 'misplaced' trust in
OL,4,Cpartner accused of baby murder, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FVarley has denied fabricating the
OL,8,F"bath incident" after a post-mortem
OL,9,Fexamination ruled out drowning as the
OL,10,Fcause of the death and instead
OL,11,Fdiscovered Preston had suffered 40
OL,12,Ftraumatic injuries.
OL,14,FMcGowan-Fazakerley told the court
OL,15,FVarley never told him about a video
OL,16,Frecording he took of Preston on the
OL,17,Fafternoon of July 27 ` while he was at
OL,18,Fwork ` over concerns the child had a
OL,19,Fseizure.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780510265
OL,3,CCo-accused 'misplaced' trust in
OL,4,Cpartner accused of baby murder, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FHe claimed his police interview was
OL,8,Fthe first time he saw the video.
OL,10,FHe said: "I feel like he has hidden
OL,11,Fthat from me. I don't understand why.
OL,13,F"I can recall every aspect of that day
OL,14,Ffrom the moment I opened my eyes until
OL,15,FI went to sleep. The days, weeks and
OL,16,Fmonths afterwards, all I have done is
OL,17,Freplay that day over and over and over
OL,18,Fagain.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780510265
OL,3,CCo-accused 'misplaced' trust in
OL,4,Cpartner accused of baby murder, court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"You would not forget you made that
OL,8,Fvideo. I would not forget if I had
OL,9,Fmade that video, and I don't know why
OL,10,Fhe didn't tell me."
OL,12,FMcGowan-Fazakerley confirmed that
OL,13,FVarley is now his ex-partner and
OL,14,Fdenies allowing the death of a child,
OL,15,Fthree counts of child cruelty and one
OL,16,Fcount of the sexual assault of a child.
OL,18,FVarley denies murder, manslaughter and
OL,19,Fmultiple counts of sexual offences and
OL,20,Ftaking and distributing indecent
OL,21,Fphotos of a child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
